== 發行 ==
該片原定於2015年1月2日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/amityville-the-awakening-trailer/|title=Amityville: The Awakening Trailer Opens a New Chapter of an Old Franchise|publisher=Slashfilm.com|first=Angie|last=Han|date=2014-08-22|accessdate=2016-02-16|archive-date=2014-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227062809/http://www.slashfilm.com/amityville-the-awakening-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來於2014年9月，電影的上映日被抽下<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=123122|title=Dimension Films Reshuffling Release Dates for Demonic and Amityville|publisher=|accessdate=2014-09-20|archive-date=2014-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123171546/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/123122-dimension-films-reshuffling-release-dates-for-demonic-and-amityville|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月，宣布電影將於2016年4月15日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3346211/amityville-reawakening-gets-new-release/|title=‘Amityville’ Won’t Haunt Until 2016|publisher=BloodyDisgusting.com|first=Brad|last=Miska|date=2015-05-21|accessdate=2016-02-16|archive-date=2017-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006161740/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3346211/amityville-reawakening-gets-new-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月2日，[[米拉麥克斯|米拉麥克斯]]不再是該片的製片商<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/bein-media-group-acquires-miramax-1201713199/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2016-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203120542/https://deadline.com/2016/03/bein-media-group-acquires-miramax-1201713199/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://beinmediagroup.com/article/bein-media-group-acquires-miramax/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2017-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707093613/https://beinmediagroup.com/article/bein-media-group-acquires-miramax/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

電影改定於2016年4月1日在美國上映<ref name="bloody-disgusting1">{{cite web |url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3346211/amityville-reawakening-gets-new-release/ |title='Amityville' Won't Haunt Until 2016 |publisher=Bloody-disgusting.com |date= |accessdate=2015-05-23 |archive-date=2017-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006161740/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3346211/amityville-reawakening-gets-new-release/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/657639-amityville-the-awakening-poster-revealed|title=Bella Thorne is Haunted in the Amityville: The Awakening Trailer|publisher=Comingsoon.net|first=Coming|last=Soon|date=2016-02-16|accessdate=2016-02-16|archive-date=2016-07-27|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160727131521/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/657639-amityville-the-awakening-poster-revealed%23/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但因試映的反應而延期至2017年1月6日上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3382539/amityville-the-awakening-pulled-from-release-by-dimension-films/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2017-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006162024/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3382539/amityville-the-awakening-pulled-from-release-by-dimension-films/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月16日，電影的美國上映日又再度延期至2017年6月30日<ref>{{cite web|last1=Andderson|first1=Derek|title=New Summer 2017 Release Date for AMITYVILLE: THE AWAKENING|url=http://dailydead.com/new-summer-2017-release-date-for-amityville-the-awakening/|website=Daily Dead|accessdate=2016-12-16|archive-date=2016-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161218055959/http://dailydead.com/new-summer-2017-release-date-for-amityville-the-awakening/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年6月7日，電影的上映日再次被下架<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/amityville-the-awakening-moves-off-summer-schedule-1202109296/|title=‘Amityville: The Awakening’ Moves Off Summer Schedule|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2017-06-07|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2017-06-23|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806140354/http://deadline.com/2017/06/amityville-the-awakening-moves-off-summer-schedule-1202109296/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國最終定於2017年10月12日在[[Google_Play|Google Play]]上發行，並於2017年10月28日在美國[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref name="release">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/amityville-the-awakening-to-stream-on-google-play-for-free-gets-limited-theatrical-release-1202174538/|title=‘Amityville: The Awakening’ To Stream On Google Play For Free; Gets Limited Theatrical Release|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-09-21|accessdate=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006112237/http://deadline.com/2017/09/amityville-the-awakening-to-stream-on-google-play-for-free-gets-limited-theatrical-release-1202174538/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本片最先於2017年7月27日開始在烏克蘭和中美洲等地上映。

